tes by employing more frequent surveys at index sites and incorporating environmental covariates into the process model to generate more accurate, location-specific estimates of equilibrium density. {\textcopyright} 2019 The Authors. The Journal of Wildlife Management Published by Wiley Periodicals, Inc.},
